<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Precision Engineering - Ningbo Dunfang Precision Machinery</title>
    <meta name="description" content="State-of-the-art manufacturing with tight tolerances and exceptional accuracy for demanding applications.">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo1.png" type="image/png">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        
        :root {
            --primary: #9c8b7a;
            --primary-light: #d4c4b4;
            --primary-dark: #7a6a5a;
            --accent: #b8a898;
            --dark: #2a2a2a;
            --gray-dark: #5a5a5a;
            --gray: #8a8a8a;
            --gray-light: #b8b8b8;
            --bg-dark: #1a1a1a;
            --bg-cream: #faf9f7;
            --bg-warm: #f5f3f0;
            --bg-light: #ffffff;
            --border: #e8e6e3;
            --shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--dark);
            background: var(--bg-cream);
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }
        
        .page-content {
            padding-top: 96px;
        }
        
        /* Hero Section */
        .advantage-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-warm) 0%, var(--bg-cream) 100%);
            padding: 6rem 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .advantage-hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%239c8b7a' fill-opacity='0.03'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            opacity: 0.5;
        }
        
        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .hero-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(156, 139, 122, 0.3);
        }
        
        .hero-icon i {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .hero-title {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--gray);
            max-width: 700px;
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        /* Content Section */
        .content-section {
            padding: 5rem 0;
        }
        
        .content-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        
        .content-card {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        
        .content-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px var(--shadow);
        }
        
        .content-card-icon {
            width: 56px;
            height: 56px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .content-card-icon i {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .content-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .content-card p {
            color: var(--gray);
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        /* Image Gallery */
        .image-gallery {
            margin: 4rem 0;
        }
        
        .gallery-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .gallery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .gallery-item {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            aspect-ratio: 4/3;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .gallery-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        
        .gallery-item:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        
        .gallery-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.8) 0%, transparent 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .gallery-overlay h4 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }
        
        .gallery-overlay p {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        /* Process Section */
        .process-section {
            background: var(--bg-section);
            padding: 5rem 0;
            margin: 4rem 0;
        }
        
        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        }
        
        .section-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--gray);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        .process-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        
        .process-step {
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .process-step::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 30px;
            right: -50%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--border);
        }
        
        .process-step:last-child::after {
            display: none;
        }
        
        .process-number {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .process-step h4 {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .process-step p {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--gray);
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        
        /* Navigation Buttons */
        .page-navigation {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 3rem 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            margin-top: 4rem;
        }
        
        .nav-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        
        .nav-btn:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border-color: var(--primary);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(41, 84, 214, 0.2);
        }
        
        .nav-btn i {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        
        .back-home {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .back-home:hover {
            background: var(--primary-dark);
            border-color: var(--primary-dark);
        }
        
        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .content-grid, .gallery-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
            
            .process-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .process-step::after {
                display: none;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-title {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .content-grid, .gallery-grid, .process-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .page-navigation {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1rem;
            }
            
            .nav-btn {
                width: 100%;
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--gray-light);
        }
        
        .footer-link {
            color: var(--gray-light);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .footer-link:hover {
            color: var(--primary-light);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 导航栏 -->
    <%- include('../partials/navbar', {currentPage: 'home'}) %>

    <main class="page-content">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="advantage-hero">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 lg:px-12">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <div class="hero-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h1 class="hero-title">Precision Engineering</h1>
                    <p class="hero-subtitle">State-of-the-art manufacturing with tight tolerances and exceptional accuracy for demanding applications. Our commitment to precision sets the standard in the industry.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 lg:px-12 py-12">
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
                    <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Precision Engineering</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                            Dunfang's precision engineering capabilities set the standard for excellence in the industry. Our state-of-the-art CNC machining centers and advanced manufacturing technology enable us to achieve tolerances as tight as ±0.001mm for critical components.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                            We specialize in producing complex geometries and intricate parts that other manufacturers cannot achieve. Our material expertise allows us to work with a wide range of materials including metals, plastics, and composites to meet specific application requirements.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                            With robust quality control processes and advanced metrology equipment, we ensure consistent results batch after batch. Our efficient production processes enable quick delivery without compromising on quality or precision.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                        <div class="relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl" style="border-radius: 8px;">
                            <img src="/images/metal-images/Flashing Forming Tool.jpg" alt="CNC Machining Center" class="w-full object-cover" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<div class=\'image-placeholder h-96 rounded-xl\'><i class=\'fas fa-industry\'></i></div>'">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Page Navigation -->
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 lg:px-12">
            <div class="page-navigation">
                <a href="/" class="nav-btn back-home">
                    <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
                    Back to Why Choose Us
                </a>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
                    <a href="/advantage/quality" class="nav-btn">
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
                        Quality Assurance
                    </a>
                    <a href="/advantage/global" class="nav-btn">
                        Global Reach
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>